     2→//! ChirpPulse – Sentiment Analysis Module
     3→//! --------------------------------------
     4→//! This module implements a pluggable sentiment–analysis subsystem that can be
     5→//! hot-swapped at runtime.  It follows the Strategy Pattern, allowing data-science
     6→//! teams to experiment with new algorithms without redeploying the entire data
     7→//! pipeline.
     8→//!
     9→//! The key abstraction is `SentimentAnalyzer`: an async-capable trait whose
    10→//! implementations score a message in real time.  A thread-safe `AnalyzerRegistry`
    11→//! stores live implementations, while `SentimentWorker` applies them to inbound
    12→//! social messages coming from upstream Kafka consumers.
    13→//!
    14→//! Dependencies (Cargo.toml):
    15→//! ```toml
    16→//! [dependencies]
    17→//! tokio        = { version = "1", features = ["full"] }
    18→//! anyhow       = "1"
    19→//! parking_lot  = "0.12"
    20→//! tracing      = "0.1"
    21→//! serde        = { version = "1", features = ["derive"] }
