# Solution: rust_data_streaming_expert_013_cross_file_refactoring_expert_01

## Key Files Identified

- /app/project/src/module_79.txt - Quality-Control & Enrichment module with Kafka streaming logic, contains `QualityRule` trait, `KafkaJsonSink`, `QualityPipeline`, and data source event stream functions
- /app/project/src/module_41.txt - Data-quality enforcement micro-service with `QualityController`, Kafka consumer/producer setup, and orchestration logic
- /app/project/src/module_1.txt - Sentiment Analysis module with analyzer registry and worker patterns (potential injection point)
- /app/project/src/utils.txt - Shared utilities including `retry_async`, `spawn_named_task`, and common patterns
- /app/project/tests/test_main.txt - Integration tests for the pipeline with mock enrichers
- /app/project/tests/test_utils.txt - Utility tests for WeightedMovingAverage, RateLimitedExecutor, retry_async

## Code Evidence

